{"product_id":"vision-support-3-bottles","title":"Vision Support 3 Boxes","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThis 3-box value bundle contains 90 softgels, or 90 days of suggested use.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEyetamins® by OPTASE® Vision Support™\u003c\/strong\u003e is an eye health supplement formulated to support macular health and help maintain clear, sharp vision. Vision Support provides a comprehensive macular nutrition vision supplement in one well-tolerated, once-daily softgel, rather than single-nutrient eye vitamin. Built for daily use, it supports macular nutrition in one step.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDAILY VISION SUPPORT\u003c\/strong\u003e: Once-daily softgels with lutein, zinc contributing to normal visual function, zeaxanthin, and astaxanthin to help support macular health, enhance eye health and help maintain clear, sharp vision in one well-tolerated dose\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eCLINICALLY BACKED INGREDIENTS:\u003c\/strong\u003e Formulated with the trusted nutrients FloraGLO® lutein and AstaPure® astaxanthin, plus an independently tested formula for confidence in quality and consistency\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eANTIOXIDANT:\u003c\/strong\u003e Carotenoids, like astaxanthin, along with Vitamin C, E, Zinc and Copper contribute to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Vitamin D supports a normal inflammatory response, important in macular health\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUse as directed.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor adults one (1) softgel per day with a meal\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not exceed recommended daily dose.A dietary supplement is not a substitute for a healthy varied diet and lifestyle.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoftgels are designed for easy swallowing and a smooth, non-chalky experience while supporting bioavailability.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach box includes 30 softgels for a 30-day supply. Softgel shell is made with bovine gelatin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAllergen information: the product contains soybeans\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEyetamins® by OPTASE® is part of the OPTASE® Eye Care System.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAscorbic Acid, Gelatin (Bovine), Refined Soybean Oil, Coconut Oil, Glycerin, Hydrogenated Soybean Oil, Safflower Oil, D-alpha-Tocopherol, Astaxanthin Oleoresin (from Haematococcus Pluvialis Algae), Olive Oil, Zinc Oxide, Sunflower Oil, Lutein (from Marigold flower), Soy Lecithin, Water, Cupric Sulfate, Red Iron Oxide, Zeaxanthin (from Capsicum fruit and Marigold flowers), DL-alpha-Tocopherol, Medium Chain Triglycerides, Tocopherols, Cholecalciferol. Contains: Soybeans\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product does not intend to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Eyetamins, Inc.","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":40248063295545,"sku":"FRET-VisionSupp-USx3","price":74.85,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0600\/4903\/1225\/files\/2026_March_VS_3_Boxes.png?v=1774905860","url":"https:\/\/eyetamins.co\/products\/vision-support-3-bottles","provider":"Eyetamins","version":"1.0","type":"link"}